                                <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                                <p>No official record of the substance of this meeting has been
                                    found. The information given above with respect to the meeting
                                    and the participants is taken from the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_298">p. 298</ref>. See also <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_415">p. 415</ref>.
                                    According to <persName corresp="#p_EW1">Elliott
                                        Roosevelt</persName>, p. 157, the principal subject of
                                    conversation was supply.</p>
                            </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>